name: I'm just practicing storm gameplan for krark
description: A cedh deck which is just a stepping stone on my journey to become the optimal krark sakashima player

main.name: Ad Nauseam
main.oracle_text: Reveal the top card of your library and put that card into your hand. You lose life equal to its mana value. You may repeat this process any number of times.
main.flavor_text: When the task spilled over into undeath, he stopped calling it his life's work.

card.name: Dockside Extortionist
card.oracle_text: When Dockside Extortionist enters the battlefield, create X Treasure tokens, where X is the number of artifacts and enchantments your opponents control. (Treasure tokens are artifacts with '{T}, Sacrifice this artifact: Add one mana of any color.')
card.flavor_text: A small price to keep such pretty things safe!

card.name: Flooded Strand
card.oracle_text: {T}, Pay 1 life, Sacrifice Flooded Strand: Search your library for a Plains or Island card, put it onto the battlefield, then shuffle.
card.flavor_text: Where dragons once slept, their bones now rest.

card.name: Flusterstorm
card.oracle_text:
Counter target instant or sorcery spell unless its controller pays {1}.
Storm (When you cast this spell, copy it for each spell cast before it this turn. You may choose new targets for the copies.)

card.name: Force of Will
card.oracle_text:
You may pay 1 life and exile a blue card from your hand rather than pay this spell's mana cost.
Counter target spell.
card.flavor_text: I alone determine my destiny.

card.name: Gamble
card.oracle_text: Search your library for a card, put that card into your hand, discard a card at random, then shuffle.
card.flavor_text: As she triggered yet another trap, Chira realized that what she thought was the goblin word for "easy" probably wasn't.

card.name: Gemstone Caverns
card.oracle_text:
If Gemstone Caverns is in your opening hand and you're not the starting player, you may begin the game with Gemstone Caverns on the battlefield with a luck counter on it. If you do, exile a card from your hand.
{T}: Add {C}. If Gemstone Caverns has a luck counter on it, instead add one mana of any color.

card.name: Gitaxian Probe
card.oracle_text:
({U/P} can be paid with either {U} or 2 life.)
Look at target player's hand.
Draw a card.
card.flavor_text:
"My flesh holds no secrets, monster. The spirit of Mirrodin will fight on."
—Vy Covalt, Mirran resistance

card.name: Imperial Seal
card.oracle_text: Search your library for a card, then shuffle and put that card on top. You lose 2 life.
card.flavor_text:
"Your presence at the palace this evening is required."
—Letter from Queen Marchesa

card.name: Lion's Eye Diamond
card.oracle_text: Discard your hand, Sacrifice Lion's Eye Diamond: Add three mana of any one color. Activate only as an instant.
card.flavor_text:
Held in the lion's eye
—Zhalfirin saying meaning "caught in the moment of crisis"

card.name: Lotus Petal
card.oracle_text: {T}, Sacrifice Lotus Petal: Add one mana of any color.

card.name: Mana Confluence
card.oracle_text: {T}, Pay 1 life: Add one mana of any color.
card.flavor_text: Five rivers encircle Theros, flowing with waters more ancient than the world itself.

Mana Vault doesn't untap during your untap step.
At the beginning of your upkeep, you may pay {4}. If you do, untap Mana Vault.
At the beginning of your draw step, if Mana Vault is tapped, it deals 1 damage to you.
{T}: Add {C}{C}{C}.

card.name: Marsh Flats
card.oracle_text: {T}, Pay 1 life, Sacrifice Marsh Flats: Search your library for a Plains or Swamp card, put it onto the battlefield, then shuffle.

({U/P} can be paid with either {U} or 2 life.)

"Your first mistake was thinking I would let you live long enough to make a second."
—Sarnvax, Gitaxian sective

{T}: Add one mana of any color.

card.oracle_text: Metalcraft — {T}: Add one mana of any color. Activate only if you control three or more artifacts.

card.oracle_text: Search your library for an instant or sorcery card, reveal it, then shuffle and put that card on top.

card.name: Pyroblast
card.oracle_text:
Choose one —
• Counter target spell if it's blue.
• Destroy target permanent if it's blue.
card.flavor_text: Water can be crushing, but it is predictable. Fire is always dynamic, its rage absolute and all-consuming.

card.name: Red Elemental Blast
card.oracle_text:
Choose one —
• Counter target blue spell.
• Destroy target blue permanent.
card.flavor_text: Nothing restrains a burning passion.

card.name: Sol Ring
card.oracle_text: {T}: Add {C}{C}.

({T}: Add {U} or {R}.)

card.oracle_text: Search your library for a card, put that card into your hand, then shuffle.

card.oracle_text: Add {B}{B}{B}.

"Leshrac, my liege, grant me the power I am due."
